dcterms:description: MIMIC-III is a rich Electronic Health Records (EHR) dataset widely used in the research community to perform various prediction tasks. It is composed of 40 tables, storing 534 variables and 63 relationships.
dcterms:title: MIMIC-III

dcterms:description: The Kaggle Medical Appointment No-Shows dataset consists of 110,527 labeled scheduled appointments, described by patient demographic information, appointment dates, and a flag indicating whether the patient received a reminder.
dcterms:title: Kaggle Medical Appointment No-Shows
